The paper discusses the development of a symbol table meta model for textual software languages, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of meta modeling and generation of symbol table infrastructures also involves concepts related to machine learning (cs.LG), compilers (cs.CC), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
